## Index Coverage Analysis
### Existing Indexes (Good)
Migration `00001` and `00024` provide good baseline coverage:
- `idx_appointments_clinic`, `idx_appointments_doctor`, `idx_appointments_patient`, `idx_appointments_status`, `idx_appointments_slot`
- `idx_users_clinic`, `idx_users_auth`, `idx_users_role`
